dc_description_s: Scale approximately 1:15 500 000. "Approved by the chart committee of the Admiralty." Inset: Anemo-hydrography of the monsoons according to Viconte Grenier. Map of Indian Ocean and Western Pacific showing tracks of various navigators, dates of discoveries, with relief shown pictorially. 1 map : color ; 59 x 112 cm
